{"tid":1539986,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"『林鄭是六德的雞』余黎青萍支持林鄭：雞有五德，文、武、勇、仁、信， 她還有廉潔一德。","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:49:47.000Z","uid":26619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"13f70d186bd1f327b5b0e13ba134ae3db5c9ac08","tid":1539986,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥晚上於Facebook 專頁上載競選辦資深顧問、前高官余黎青萍的影片，余黎青萍在退休前曾歷任多個機構及政府部門要職，包括廉政公署、前市政局、屋宇署及教育署等。余在片中表示，早於90年代任職衛生福利科的時候，認識林鄭。她稱讚林鄭為人爽直，做事實話實說，工作上十分投入，或會給予別人一種錯覺，認為她很冷漠。但如大家願意多花時間了解她更多，便會發現林鄭非常有愛心。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，林鄭過往在處理僭建一事上，保障公眾安全，維護法紀，要合情、合法、合理處理事件並不容易，但她可找到一個平衝點，又讚揚她除了五德兼備外，即文、武、勇、仁、信， 她還有廉潔一德，形容廉潔是作為一位領導賢才的必要條件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/1807628-余黎青萍林鄭冷漠是錯覺-讚具備五德又廉潔\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1807628-%E4%BD%99%E9%BB%8E%E9%9D%92%E8%90%8D%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%86%B7%E6%BC%A0%E6%98%AF%E9%8C%AF%E8%A6%BA-%E8%AE%9A%E5%85%B7%E5%82%99%E4%BA%94%E5%BE%B7%E5%8F%88%E5%BB%89%E6%BD%94&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcaiDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=18b50ede\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/1807628-余黎青萍林鄭冷漠是錯覺-讚具備五德又廉潔</a>"},{"pid":"e3376cb374df7e8b621537cdf2b5203321d42d30","tid":1539986,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r54hifk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr54hifk.png&h=4b46846d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xGciM8F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxGciM8F.png&h=54e1b5b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Moqr8G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Moqr8G.jpg&h=25ae8368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qc9APm2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=